an></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:%C2%AB%D0%9E%D1%82%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%87%D0%BD%D0=
%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8_%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B9%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B9_%D1%=
80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%BA%D0%B8%C2%BB_%D0%90%D0%A0%D0%9C%D0%98=
-2017_(8).jpg" class=3D"mw-file-description"><img src=3D"https://upload.wik=
imedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/54/%C2%AB%D0%9E%D1%82%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%8=
7%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8_%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B9%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BE%=
D0%B9_%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%B4%D0%BA%D0%B8%C2%BB_%D0%90%D0%A0%D=
